Shifting Sea, 2017, 39x52 inches currently on display @richardhellergallery Los Angeles thru May 6, and @hartmanfineart in Portland thru May 27. 
#seascape #beringsea #aleutiandreams #water #ocean #commercialfishing #alaska #crabbing #sea #seafood #fishwork

Tonight on PBS @frontlinepbs don't miss @4fishgreenberg new documentary 'The Fish on my Plate about the seafood industry. Should be very informative for those of you wondering which fish to choose at the market. Paul Greenberg is my favorite writer on the topic. 
This image is from a story I made with Paul a few years back for @californiasunday about the California Groundfish industry and the comeback of many species that were once (debatably) considered overfished. Shown here is a cod end full of mixed deep water species on the deck of the f/v Pioneer out of Monterey, California. The story is called 'The Fishermen's Dilemma' searchable online. 
#commercialfishing #trawling #california #groundfish #monterey #seafood #fishwork #paulgreenberg #fishermen #sea #trawl #frontline #pbs

Carcass staring contest with National Bird. 
This one didn't make it in the recent @californiasunday story @laurelsara and I made about the crazy eagle scene in Dutch Harbor, Ak but lots of weirdness still hiding in my archives. Google "dirty birds California Sunday" to check out the story online! 
#eagle #america #staringcontest #fishwork #aleutiandreams #baldeagle #dutchharbor #commercialfishing #pollock #alaska

Install shots from my Aleutian Dreams exhibition on the wall now at @hartmanfineart in Portland, Oregon. The show is up til May 27! Hope to see you there!

Also this week I'm taking over the @smithsonianmagazine Instagram account! Lots of great work over there posted by a new photog every week. Check it. 
#portland #portlandart #pdxart #aleutiandreams #coreyarnold #fishwork  #exhibition #gallery #oregon #charlesahartmanfineart ##art

Funding for scientific research and fisheries management in Alaska is the reason why fish stocks in Alaskan waters remain healthy and sustainable, unlike many other examples around the world where overfishing has taken a toll. I support science based management even if I'm not always happy with temporarily smaller quotas and fishing restrictions. In the long game, we all win. #marchforscience #commercialfishing #resist #beringsea #alaska #trawler #atkamackerel #aleutiandreams #aleutians #fishing #arctic #alaskaseafood #seafood #boat

Portrait of a hybrid Opilio/Bairdi crab caught in the Bering Sea before being released back into the sea. These crab are feisty even during their first ever view of life above water. ---------------------------------
Crustacean Resistance, 20x27 inches, print on display at @richardhellergallery Santa Monica thru May 6 and @hartmanfineart thru May 28. Click my profile link to view the series.
